# Nobel Prize Search API

Ingest Nobel Prize laureate data into MongoDB and provide a Flask API with fuzzy and text-based searches, all inside of Docker.

## Prerequisites

- Docker & Docker Compose  
- Python 3.7+ to run `ingest.py` locally

## Run
- If you plan to run this via bash, then please run:
```bash
run.sh
```

- This will run the bash script, testing different types of searches, and also test and provide na upsert.